asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Gnu-Ladies-Choice-C2PBTX-Womens-Snowboard-2013/270937P,default,pd.html  The GNU Ladies Choice snowboard is the pinnacle of womens shred sticks. Combines GNU three best technologies of C2BTX, Magnetraction and Pickle Tech and you will have a snowboard that is capable of anything your mind can create. With balance through asymmetry sidecuts are perfectly balance, with added C2BTX you get the performance of camber in the tip and tail for big landings and takeouts while rockered between your feet for catch free fun and added Magnetraction gives you extra contact points giving you unbelievable control all over the mountain. Tested and proven by Jamie Anderson the GNU Ladies Choice will handle the most insane park lines or the most technical free riding, while making sure no matter what your riding is effortless and filled with joy.
